\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 11. Write an SQL query to print the name of employees having the highest salary in each department.\
SELECT W.DEPARTMENT, W.FIRST_NAME, W.SALARY\
FROM Worker W\
INNER JOIN (\
    SELECT DEPARTMENT, MAX(SALARY) AS MAX_SALARY\
    FROM Worker\
    GROUP BY DEPARTMENT\
) AS DEPT_MAX\
ON W.DEPARTMENT = DEPT_MAX.DEPARTMENT \
AND W.SALARY = DEPT_MAX.MAX_SALARY;\
